# 🎮 EmuHub – Android Emulation Central

[![Website](https://img.shields.io/badge/🌐-Live_Demo-4f8ef7)](https://your-demo-link.com)  
[![GitHub release](https://img.shields.io/github/v/release/YOUR_USERNAME/emuhub)](https://github.com/YOUR_USERNAME/emuhub/releases)

**One place for GPU drivers, Winlator mods, game patches, and every tool you need to run PC games on Android.**

EmuHub is a community‑friendly static web app that centralises the best resources for Android PC emulation. It automatically fetches the latest **Turnip Gen8 (A8xx) driver** from `StevenMXZ/Adreno-Tools-Drivers` and provides quick access to Winlator forks, GameHub, DXVK, VKD3D, Box64, and more.

![Screenshot](https://via.placeholder.com/800x400?text=EmuHub+Screenshot)  
*(Add a real screenshot of your live page)*

---

## ✨ Features

- 🔥 **Auto‑updated A8xx driver** – always shows the newest `Turnip_Gen8_*.zip` for Snapdragon 8 Elite / 8s Elite.
- 🎮 **Turnip GPU drivers** – links for Adreno 6xx, 7xx, and Mesa Zink.
- 🪟 **Winlator builds** – Official, Cmod, Ludashi, and more.
- 🛠 **GameHub & tools** – GameHub, GameNative, BannerHub, DXVK, VKD3D, Box64, FexCore.
- 📱 **Fully responsive** – works on desktop, tablet, and mobile (buttons stack on small screens).
- ⚡ **Quick‑start guide** – 5 steps to run Windows games on Android.

---

## 🚀 How to use the live site

1. Open `index.html` in any modern browser.
2. The featured card automatically fetches the latest A8xx driver ZIP.
3. Click any **Download** button to go to the respective GitHub release.
4. Follow the **Quick‑Start Guide** to set up Winlator and import the Turnip driver.

> **Note:** The GitHub API is used to fetch the latest release. If you run the page locally, CORS may block the request – host it on GitHub Pages or a local server for full functionality.

